                                                                                    Fortis Inc. - Strategy and SWOT Report, is a source of comprehensive company data and information. The report covers the company’s structure, operation, SWOT analysis, product and service offerings and corporate actions, providing a 360° view of the company.Features:- Detailed information on Fortis Inc. required for business and competitor intelligence needs- A study of the major internal and external factors affecting Fortis Inc. in the form of a SWOT analysis- An in-depth view of the business model of Fortis Inc. including a breakdown and examination of key business segments- Intelligence on Fortis Inc.’s mergers and acquisitions (M&A), strategic partnerships and alliances, capital raising, private equity transactions, and financial and legal advisors- News about Fortis Inc., such as business expansion, restructuring, and contract wins- Large number of easy-to-grasp charts and graphs that present important data and key trendsHighlights:Fortis Inc. (Fortis or ‘the company’) is an international electric and gas utility holding company. It is engaged in the generation, transmission, and distribution of electricity through its subsidiaries. In addition, the company is engaged in the distribution of natural gas and in the operation of hotels and commercial real estate. The company operates in Canada, the Caribbean countries, and the US. It is headquartered in St. John's, Canada, and employed 7,660 people as of December 31, 2014.Reasons to Purchase:- Gain understanding of Fortis Inc. and the factors that influence its strategies- Track strategic initiatives of the company and latest corporate news and actions- Assess Fortis Inc. as a prospective partner, vendor or supplier- Support sales activities by understanding your customers' businesses better- Stay up to date on Fortis Inc.’s business structure, strategy and prospects
                                                                                

