We are investing in safe, clean and reliable energy solutions
We are committed to serving our customers and our communities
Learn more about our responsible stewardship.



 
Fortis is now listed on the New York Stock Exchange
From a local Newfoundland and Labrador business to a leader in the North American Electric and Gas Utility Industry
View video of Fortis NYSE bell ringing on October 18, 2016



Our people are our strength 
Best-in-class, talented and committed people who know the business and confidently serve the needs of our customers each and every day




43 years of consecutive dividend payment increases

Learn more about investing in Fortis



We own 10 utility operations in 17 locations in Canada, the United States and the Caribbean
Our 8,000 employees are proud to safely deliver reliable, cost-effective energy to our customers
Learn more about Fortis companies



 
Fortis powers ahead with a significant investment in transmission
Fortis completes acquisition of the largest independent transmission utility  in the United States for US$11.8 billion




We are a leader in the North American Electric and Gas Utility Industry
From our beginnings as a small, provincial utility we have grown and transformed our company to approximately $48 billion in assets, bringing energy to over 3 million customers
Learn more about Fortis

































Fortis  is one of the top 15 utilities in North America

We have grown from just $390 million in assets when we were formed in 1987 to  approximately $48 billion today. Fortis continues to power ahead as we seek additional opportunities to diversify our asset base and grow our company both within our existing franchise territories and beyond.
Learn more about Fortis











